# Dataset Information

This project uses a Quick Commerce transactional dataset containing approximately **1,000,000 orders**.

Due to GitHub file size limitations, the complete dataset has not been included in this repository.

Dataset Summary:

- Records: ~1,000,000
- Attributes: 13
- Format: CSV
- Size: ~90 MB

The dataset contains:

- Order ID
- Company
- City
- Customer Age
- Order Value
- Delivery Time
- Distance
- Items Count
- Product Category
- Payment Method
- Customer Rating
- Discount Applied
- Delivery Partner Rating
